---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Yatish | The Engineer-Designer">
  
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Less "Pixel Pusher."<br/>
        More <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600">Product Architect.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        I bring a Computer Engineering background to UI/UX. I speak the language of developers, the strategy of C-suite, and the empathy of users.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 md:grid-rows-3 gap-6 h-auto md:h-[800px]">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 relative group rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531403009284-440f080d1e12?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Yatish Facilitating Workshop" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full mb-3">Leadership</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Facilitation over Dictation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-md text-sm">
            My management style isn't about sitting in an office. It's about being at the whiteboard, untangling complexity with the team, and bridging the gap between design and dev.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-500">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Yatish Professional" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-indigo-900/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
          <p class="text-white font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">Stakeholder Management</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-center border border-indigo-100 hover:border-indigo-200 transition-colors relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-indigo-200 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10 opacity-50"></div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-indigo-600 mb-2">35%</h3>
        <p class="text-indigo-900 font-bold mb-4">OpEx Reduction</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Design isn't just art; it's economics. I focus on metrics that move the needle for the business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group rounded-3xl bg-slate-900 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between text-white overflow-hidden relative shadow-lg">
        <svg class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
          <path d="M10 90 Q 50 10 90 90" stroke-width="2" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Fuel</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2">RedBull Racing Fan</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-4">
          I love the precision of F1. Just like in UX, split-second decisions and system optimization define the winner.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 flex items-center gap-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl flex-shrink-0">
          ☕️
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Powered by Indian Chai</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            When I'm not designing, you'll find me exploring astronomy or brewing the perfect chai. I believe the best ideas happen away from the screen.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Ready to optimize your design operations?</h2>
      <a href="mailto:yatish.designer@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-slate-900 border border-transparent rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-600">
        Let's Talk Strategy
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>